ghteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11210,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/08\/ibn-umar-kharijites-ayat-takfir\/","url_meta":{"origin":25256,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Umar on Rebels: Khawarij apply verses about unbelievers on Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, considered the Khawarij rebels to be the worst of Allah\u2019s creation and he said, \u201cIndeed, they take verses that were revealed about unbelievers and use them against believers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6531 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43485,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/04\/05\/umar-murder-conspiracy\/","url_meta":{"origin":25256,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Murder: Groups executed for conspiring to kill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: A young boy was murdered in an act of treachery. Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf the people of San\u2019a\u2019 had conspired to do this, I would execute all of them.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 9\/8 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/27\/umar-ibn-al-khattab-inspired\/","url_meta":{"origin":25256,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Umar: If anyone in Ummah is divinely-inspired, it is Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBefore you were nations with divinely inspired people. If such a person were in my nation, it would surely be Umar.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3689 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3657,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/13\/umar-ibn-abdul-aziz-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":25256,"position":4},"title":"Umar II on Faith: Islam is fulfilled by duties, limits, traditions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, faith consists of obligations, laws, limits, and traditions. Whoever perfects them has perfected faith, and whoever does not perfect them will not have perfect faith.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1\/11 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\